      • getFreeColGameObjectIterator

        public java.util.Iterator<FreeColGameObject> getFreeColGameObjectIterator()
        Gets an Iterator over every registered FreeColGameObject. This Iterator should be iterated once in a while since it cleans the FreeColGameObject cache. Very few routines call this any more, so there is a thresholded call in removeFreeColGameObject to ensure the cache is still cleaned. Reconsider this if the situation changes.
        Returns:
        An Iterator containing every registered FreeColGameObject.
